<td bgcolor="#404070" width="100%">
<img src="/forums/images/icons/icon0.gif" border="0" height="15" width="15" alt="icon">
<font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2"  color="#FFFFFF"><b> 12-18-03 Patch Message</b></font>
<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1">
<b> Posted by: [<a href="/forums/member.php?s=6776fe9b5ca000b30e639b244efb6c1c&action=mailform&userid=15">Brael</a>] on 12-19-2003 @ 10:35 PM</b>
